.engram/
```

### 6. `<repo>/.cursorignore`

Create or update:
```
.agent-output/
.engram/
build/
node_modules/
vendor/
```

## Verify global setup

Before creating project files, verify the global setup exists:
```bash
ls ~/.cursor/rules/000-project-bootstrap.mdc && echo "Global setup OK"
```
If missing, tell the user: "Global agent setup not found. Clone ai-resources to ~/.cursor/ first."

## After setup

Report what was created and remind the user:
- "Run `/self-update` to keep shared resources current"
- "Global resources at `~/.cursor/` вЂ” project config at `<repo>/.cursorrules` and `<repo>/.cursor/mcp.json`"
- "All workflows, rules, skills, roles, and personas are global and shared across projects"
